{"id":184375,"date":"2023-08-04T17:15:14","date_gmt":"2023-08-04T11:45:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=184375"},"modified":"2023-08-04T17:17:50","modified_gmt":"2023-08-04T11:47:50","slug":"kiran-bhatt-pooja-bhatts-mother","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kiran-bhatt-pooja-bhatts-mother\/","title":{"rendered":"Kiran Bhatt (Pooja Bhatt&#8217;s Mother) Wiki, Age, Husband, Family, Biography &#038; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-and-Pooja-Bhatt.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-184673 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-and-Pooja-Bhatt.jpg\" alt=\"An old picture of Kiran Bhatt and Pooja Bhatt\" width=\"508\" height=\"468\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-and-Pooja-Bhatt.jpg 645w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-and-Pooja-Bhatt-300x276.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 508px) 100vw, 508px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Kiran Bhatt is a British citizen who is known for being the mother of the Indian actress and film director <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/pooja-bhatt\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pooja Bhatt<\/a> and the ex-wife of the Indian film director and producer <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/krishna-bhatt\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mahesh Bhatt<\/a>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bcdf36bccbe\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bcdf36bccbe\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kiran-bhatt-pooja-bhatts-mother\/#WikiBiography\" title=\"Wiki\/Biography\">Wiki\/Biography<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kiran-bhatt-pooja-bhatts-mother\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kiran-bhatt-pooja-bhatts-mother\/#Family\" title=\"Family\">Family<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kiran-bhatt-pooja-bhatts-mother\/#Parents_Siblings\" title=\"Parents &amp; Siblings\">Parents &amp; Siblings<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kiran-bhatt-pooja-bhatts-mother\/#Husband_Children\" title=\"Husband &amp; Children\">Husband &amp; Children<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kiran-bhatt-pooja-bhatts-mother\/#Kiran_Bhatt_and_Mahesh_Bhatts_Love_Story\" title=\"Kiran Bhatt and Mahesh Bhatt&#8217;s Love Story\">Kiran Bhatt and Mahesh Bhatt&#8217;s Love Story<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kiran-bhatt-pooja-bhatts-mother\/#The_Love_Triangle\" title=\"The Love Triangle\">The Love Triangle<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kiran-bhatt-pooja-bhatts-mother\/#FactsTrivia\" title=\"Facts\/Trivia\">Facts\/Trivia<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Wiki\/Biography<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Kiran Bhatt was born as Lorraine Bright <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_184375_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_184375_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/CQ7jFq0hqu4\/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Pooja Bhatt &#8211; Instagram<\/a><\/span><\/span> on Thursday,\u00a05 July 1951 (<strong>age 72 years; as of 2023<\/strong>). Kiran Bhatt is of English, Scottish, Burmese, and Armenian descent. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_184375_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_184375_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.herzindagi.com\/society-culture\/pooja-bhatt-unknown-facts-mahesh-bhatt-elder-daughter-article-171813\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Her Zindagi<\/a><\/span><\/span> Her zodiac sign is Cancer.\u00a0She did her schooling at Bombay Scottish Orphanage in Mumbai. While she was studying in school, Mahesh often used to visit her secretly, and once they got caught, Kiran was expelled from the school. Later, Mahesh got her enrolled at the YWCA, where she learned typing. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_184375_1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_184375_1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/indiannewsweekly.com\/2021\/03\/31\/mahesh-bhatt-love-story-lorraine-bright-pooja-bhatt-mother-lorraine-bright-kiran-and-mahesh-bhatt-love-story-had-all-the-shades-of-grey\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Indian News Weekly<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Physical Appearance<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Height (approx.): <\/strong>5&#8242; 7&#8243;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour: <\/strong>Golden Brown<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour: <\/strong>Hazel Brown<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-184675\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt.jpg\" alt=\"An old picture of Kiran Bhatt\" width=\"395\" height=\"422\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt.jpg 577w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-281x300.jpg 281w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 395px) 100vw, 395px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Family<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>She belongs to a Roman Catholic family. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_184375_1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_184375_1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.bollywoodshaadis.com\/articles\/love-life-of-mahesh-bhatt-7283\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Bollywood Shaadis<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Parents_Siblings\"><\/span><strong>Parents &amp; Siblings<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Not much is known about her parents &amp; siblings.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Husband_Children\"><\/span><strong>Husband &amp; Children<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Lorraine Bright got married to the Indian film director and producer Mahesh Bhatt in 1968 as per Arya Samaj traditions. After their marriage, she changed her name to Kiran Bhatt. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_184375_1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_184375_1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.bollywoodshaadis.com\/articles\/pooja-bhatt-used-to-hate-soni-razdan-for-snatching-her-father-mahesh-bhatt-15948\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Bollywood Shaadis<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_184678\" style=\"width: 427px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/A-wedding-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-and-Mahesh-Bhatt.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-184678\" class=\" wp-image-184678\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/A-wedding-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-and-Mahesh-Bhatt.jpg\" alt=\"A wedding picture of Kiran Bhatt and Mahesh Bhatt\" width=\"417\" height=\"429\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/A-wedding-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-and-Mahesh-Bhatt.jpg 599w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/A-wedding-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-and-Mahesh-Bhatt-292x300.jpg 292w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-184678\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A wedding picture of Kiran Bhatt and Mahesh Bhatt<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Together, they have a daughter named <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/pooja-bhatt\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pooja Bhatt<\/a> and a son named Rahul Bhatt. While Pooja is an actress and film director, Rahul is a fitness trainer.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_184679\" style=\"width: 438px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-Mahesh-Bhatt-and-Pooja-Bhatt.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-184679\" class=\" wp-image-184679\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-Mahesh-Bhatt-and-Pooja-Bhatt.jpg\" alt=\"An old picture of Kiran Bhatt, Mahesh Bhatt, and Pooja Bhatt\" width=\"428\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-Mahesh-Bhatt-and-Pooja-Bhatt.jpg 616w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-Mahesh-Bhatt-and-Pooja-Bhatt-300x265.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 428px) 100vw, 428px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-184679\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">An old picture of Kiran Bhatt, Mahesh Bhatt, and Pooja Bhatt<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_184681\" style=\"width: 513px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Kiran-Bhatt-with-her-children.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-184681\" class=\" wp-image-184681\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Kiran-Bhatt-with-her-children.jpg\" alt=\"Kiran Bhatt with her children\" width=\"503\" height=\"498\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Kiran-Bhatt-with-her-children.jpg 584w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Kiran-Bhatt-with-her-children-300x297.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Kiran-Bhatt-with-her-children-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Kiran-Bhatt-with-her-children-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 503px) 100vw, 503px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-184681\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kiran Bhatt with her children<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_184682\" style=\"width: 539px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Kiran-Bhatt-with-her-family.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-184682\" class=\" wp-image-184682\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Kiran-Bhatt-with-her-family.jpg\" alt=\"Kiran Bhatt with her family\" width=\"529\" height=\"438\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Kiran-Bhatt-with-her-family.jpg 667w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Kiran-Bhatt-with-her-family-300x248.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 529px) 100vw, 529px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-184682\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kiran Bhatt with her family<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Although Mahesh and Kiran mutually separated in the early 80s, Mahesh stayed legally wedded to Kiran as he didn&#8217;t want to alienate his wife and children. Since Mahesh did not divorce Kiran, he later, adopted his mother&#8217;s faith in order to marry Soni Razdan. Mahesh has two daughters with Soni, Shaheen Bhatt and <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/alia-bhatt\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Alia Bhatt<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kiran_Bhatt_and_Mahesh_Bhatts_Love_Story\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Kiran Bhatt and Mahesh Bhatt&#8217;s Love Story<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Kiran Bhatt first met Mahesh Bhatt when she was in school. Their friendship grew with time and the two soon fell in love with each other. In the beginning of their relationship, Mahesh often used to visit her school to secretly meet her. In an interview, while talking about the same, Mahesh said,<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>I would jump across the wall to meet her but, when we got caught, she had to leave the orphanage. I got her enrolled at the YWCA so that she could become a typist and fend for herself. All along, I kept working. I made ads for Dalda and Lifebuoy.&#8221;<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>They dated each other for a while before getting married to each other. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_184375_1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[6]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_184375_1_6\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.bollywoodshaadis.com\/articles\/love-life-of-mahesh-bhatt-7283\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Bollywood Shaadis<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_184684\" style=\"width: 495px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-with-Mahesh-Bhatt.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-184684\" class=\" wp-image-184684\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-with-Mahesh-Bhatt.jpg\" alt=\"An old picture of Kiran Bhatt with Mahesh Bhatt\" width=\"485\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-with-Mahesh-Bhatt.jpg 589w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/An-old-picture-of-Kiran-Bhatt-with-Mahesh-Bhatt-300x243.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 485px) 100vw, 485px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-184684\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">An old picture of Kiran Bhatt with Mahesh Bhatt<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Love_Triangle\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">The Love Triangle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Mahesh Bhatt&#8217;s relationship with her wife Kiran Bhatt went sour in the late 70s when he got involved in an extra-marital affair with the Indian actress Praveen Babi. It was the same time when Mahesh delivered back-to-back flops. In an interview, Mahesh confessed,<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>I was married to Kiran, had a child, and was responsible for both of them. Still, my physical self was drawn to another woman.&#8221;<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>Soon, Mahesh left Kiran Bhatt for Parveen. Apparently, after two-and-a-half years of romance, Mahesh and Parveen got separated. Following his separation from Parveen, Mahesh returned to Kiran but by that time Kiran had grown distant from him. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_184375_1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[7]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_184375_1_7\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.bollywoodshaadis.com\/articles\/love-life-of-mahesh-bhatt-7283\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Bollywood Shaadis<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FactsTrivia\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Facts\/Trivia<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Mahesh Bhatt&#8217;s first real success Arth (1982) was loosely autobiographical, and it stemmed from the love triangle involving his wife, Kiran Bhatt, and Parveen Babi.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_184670\" style=\"width: 270px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Arth-film-poster.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-184670\" class=\"size-full wp-image-184670\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Arth-film-poster.jpg\" alt=\"Arth film poster\" width=\"260\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Arth-film-poster.jpg 260w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Arth-film-poster-222x300.jpg 222w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 260px) 100vw, 260px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-184670\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Arth film poster<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>One of Mahesh Bhatt&#8217;s biggest successes, Aashiqui (1990), was based on his relationship with Kiran Bhatt.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_184672\" style=\"width: 278px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Aashiqui-film-poster.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-184672\" class=\"size-full wp-image-184672\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Aashiqui-film-poster.jpg\" alt=\"Aashiqui film poster\" width=\"268\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Aashiqui-film-poster.jpg 268w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Aashiqui-film-poster-216x300.jpg 216w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 268px) 100vw, 268px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-184672\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Aashiqui film poster<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In an interview, while talking about her parents troubled relationship, Pooja Bhatt said,<br \/>\n<blockquote><p>I\u2019ve been very lucky that I\u2019ve not had a really traumatic childhood. Okay, Mom and Dad used to fight and there would be utter chaos at times at home, but I would only be a silent spectator to all this. I was too young to do anything about it. Of course, it did have some psychological effect on me, but then I guess I was growing up and learnt to accept it as part of my life. My parents never hid anything from me. They saw to it that I didn\u2019t suffer because of their differences and I got the best of both the worlds. So, where\u2019s the trauma?\u201d<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Revealing how her parents&#8217; disturbed relationship had a psychological effect on her, Pooja, in an interview, said,<br \/>\n<blockquote><p>You know. What spoils a marriage or a relationship is permanence! When one starts seeking permanence in a relationship then that\u2019s the end of it. Nothing ever remains the same! One has to adjust to the changing times. I do not blame only my Dad or my mom for that matter for their split. Both are equally to blame for their soured relationship. For it takes two hands to clap. Sometimes when I look around and see marriages breaking up, I get very disillusioned by this whole institution. But then I think it is up to the individuals to make a marriage work.\u201d<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In an interview, when asked about her mother seeking companionship or considering remarriage, Pooja Bhatt replied that her mother was very attractive and a lot of men approached her to ask her out. Further she said that although she went out for parties and dinners sometimes, her mother never got emotionally attached to someone again in her life. She added that her mother was very happy in her life and didn&#8217;t want to mess with marriage once again.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In an interview, Pooja revealed that although she was deeply angered by her father&#8217;s choice to take marital vows with another woman while still being married to her mother, it was her mother, Kiran, who advised her not to harbour any resentment or hatred towards Mahesh. Lorraine emphasized that Mahesh is fundamentally a good man, and that&#8217;s why Pooja should never develop feelings of hatred towards him.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>According to some sources, Kiran Bhatt passed away in 2003 at the age of 66. However, some other sources claim that she is alive and residing in England. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_184375_1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[8]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_184375_1_8\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/timesofindia.indiatimes.com\/entertainment\/hindi\/bollywood\/news\/pooja-bhatt-remembers-mother-kiran-bhatt-on-her-birth-anniversary-with-a-stunning-throwback-photo-fans-react\/articleshow\/92675408.cms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Times of India<\/a><\/span><\/span> <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_184375_1_9\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[9]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_184375_1_9\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.medadmbjmc.in\/death-cause-kiran-bhatt-mahesh-bhatt-ex-wife\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">MEDADM<\/a><\/span><\/span> <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_184375_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_184375_1_10\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[10]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_184375_1_10\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.news9live.com\/entertainme