_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.medadmbjmc.in\/death-cause-kiran-bhatt-mahesh-bhatt-ex-wife\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">MEDADM<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_184375_1_10\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>10<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.news9live.com\/entertainment\/mahesh-bhatts-top-controversies-converting-to-islam-kiran-bhatt-parveen-babi-cheating-scandal-kissing-daughter-pooja-and-more-2235513\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">News Nine<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n <\/tbody> <\/table> <\/div><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Kiran Bhatt is a British citizen who is known for being the mother of the Indian actress and film director Pooja Bhatt and the ex-wife of the Indian film director and producer Mahesh Bhatt. Wiki\/Biography Kiran Bhatt was born as Lorraine Bright Pooja Bhatt &#8211; Instagram on Thursday,\u00a05 July 1951 (age 72 years; as of 2023). Kiran Bhatt is of English, Scottish, Burmese, and Armenian descent. Her Zindagi Her zodiac sign is Cancer.\u00a0She did her schooling at Bombay Scottish Orphanage in Mumbai. While she was studying in school, Mahesh often used to visit her secretly, and once they got caught, <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":23,"featured_media":184673,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/184375"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/23"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.i